F7E7duFJAsOFs4d17xlbOL8xu1krIH9zhgM7HuvnxpH_rDdImFzlQnO8PHe8dHLXGFEhjGtwjcZUqmO3xXX3eRKIY4bqLxbNF0QiWF9ajhEnqbfvlyK1ibiGoOQBQKrb-qJsFpJo9E5uS-MhoNaZJCTjF-1wJYBJQseydqo6tTJA/A-r0e1FurPNdmbbAzO5y1K__GjslRr1r/19" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;em style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;在此处&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;注册&lt;em style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;。&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;面对美以联合攻击，伊朗的战略是对华盛顿在波斯湾的盟友进行报复。它&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/hmmPp_OFcdrd5oLhLWVXYi--zXeBjGij4RFgioalu1YGxcgPcDAZfseylKKDgrEqM4ajf8FYMoIw-BTxa5yor81KzjVUIfCTNpbAjfIBwEy8XeeWePB5MTxpFtuUaQ_Hh9Lo4Yskspt2PHnMoSFtPggKXHEAsgqIRBmhofEcK17DWddPlFNFONqT-8NyhKUVtpR2WPEdMEBgITtM9mLsGk74Maa7SLx4pJtHi2LSdwFcPT1i1jI9ZlWeqgHrXFPdsh02kdZVsmQO4FlKwloQ1tapJQCosU96FQpjSzhevKmwIUNRxhGZrUomwCC32u3fW208HvzHUUf52fc4sO-9PwgewQL0cstANcCJf2wvqgF1ErQUqTKqH3JqJyzai51XzLvOsKt8ri8B4gHwzw2wVjbV2vUM_-XwYB-p4hIXLAtRbnLnax1HeSO7UU70-qvmH-OTJvYyaBBsK5tw63Eivxfk1M3soDTGG7Q095-oVCso0-qF3d_4aW2GOuoJl3rRAN2dAqWC/TDOd9r99dnqwMlo41GDuovVatowcUiaU/19" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="以色列誓言保留能源基地后，伊朗继续发动海湾袭击"&gt;袭击了能源基础设施&lt;/a&gt;，对石油市场造成严重破坏，并停止了通过霍尔木兹海峡的运输，给全球经济带来了冲击。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;本周以色列对伊朗南帕尔斯气田的袭击——事态升级，促使伊朗伊斯兰共和国对卡塔尔的液化天然气中心造成严重破坏作为回应——可能只会让冲突&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/1qY2EVMjTGdbUIWFpgk0rraR_ywyJmtR9WvM0cdv0l_EXJzooXOr3T1pybJmTuuE3WlhFds03KlpeGKnq7qT0Q8v8el2u1RDDA_5gigj881QO0EU_3hcj_yhGvSsePgi-qVneOdhqO0q5aVss5ZcyBBu_qXefTMUCTaBFKPOt_1eK_loXTEgDDv_xjkQIR6XmnLhAeQUTSRT4n4Aa6hxwXh0VilCts0uB78BhOhW954jg7Uwjk1xNB4JvS5j55Pawl3pBl58RrZCLOTp936J1omeMB4-enGbmws5TI0zvWTJrytVX6SaDfO_jDVLOXci5Ra0OcDrPSdoTjWSE0_AACifxXPflRJICpvOFODveEoCXmKLgggxXc2PqDISMbPQ4fuN15bUeIE95J_tO4v_Kw0zxTZ1H9RHbF7VXDjFrGjBAI-GLUngNBGOGzJqHkzKxJ5uowwKuZX6PKoG09Tsfpp1Ixd6ZkP6z_fgMDuVLrbdIq5U1stFqUV_Z3W9Kp7qmBdcHQN69h0Sx8u42F4l7h7JCsDbhxKQ/5wcJplbUHT3AJgIzpXkIV2O6t2telPJO/19" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="伊朗让孤立的特朗普陷入历史性的石油危机"&gt;各方&lt;/a&gt;缩减战争的范围和潜在的破坏性。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure style="margin: 20px 0;"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="580"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/izPGIHCIoI2g/v0/-1x-1.jpg" alt="TEHRAN, IRAN - MARCH 18: Large crowds gather during a joint funeral held for Ali Larijani, Secretary of Iran&amp;amp;#39;s Supreme National Security Council, Basij commander Major General Gholam Soleimani, and 84 sailors from the Iranian Navy frigate IRIS Dena, on March 18, 2026 in Tehran, Iran. Larijani and Gholamreza, two of the highest-ranking Iranian officials to be assassinated since the outbreak of the war on February 28, were killed in US-Israeli airstrikes on March 17, according to Iranian state media. The 84 sailors were killed when the IRIS Dena was sunk in a torpedo strike by the USSCharlotte, an American submarine,off the coast of Sri Lanka on March 4. (Photo by Majid Saeedi&amp;amp;#x2F;Getty Images) Photographer: Majid Saeedi&amp;amp;#x2F;Getty Images Europe" width="580"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="伊朗德黑兰 - 3 月 18 日：2026 年 3 月 18 日，伊朗最高国家安全委员会秘书阿里·拉里贾尼、巴斯基指挥官古拉姆·苏莱马尼少将和伊朗海军护卫舰 IRIS Dena 的 84 名水兵在伊朗德黑兰举行联合葬礼，大批人群聚集在一起。据伊朗官方媒体报道，拉里贾尼和古拉姆雷扎是自2月28日战争爆发以来被暗杀的两名伊朗最高官员，他们于3月17日在美以空袭中身亡。 3 月 4 日，IRIS Dena 号在斯里兰卡海岸被美国潜艇夏洛特号的鱼雷击沉，造成 84 名船员死亡。（摄影：Majid Saeedi&amp;amp;#x2F;Getty Images） 摄影师：Majid Saeedi&amp;amp;#x2F;Getty Images Europe" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/izPGIHCIoI2g/v0/-1x-1.jpg" style="width: 100%; display: block; margin-bottom: 4px;" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;figcaption&gt;&lt;div style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4;"&gt;周三，人群在德黑兰参加伊朗最高国家安全委员会秘书阿里·拉里贾尼等人的联合葬礼。&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figcaption&gt;&lt;div style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4; font-style: italic;"&gt;摄影师：Majid Saeedi/Getty Images Europe&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;美国财政部长斯科特·贝森特昨天表示， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/f2rFsPQ07LaBJACSWrFHEEk_GMOi4f08clQ7FXHkpYNREXgUGRZL6GgLCdOET0FWpbn5pvHwUL0ftPiLRGv8Wceykty0Ke8ocAeeMSLi7WknmimtceuUxyevZgQyjgqEYu8BNZvCUaYfTy9GOOkgSY1bpsmhj-fu3F6JeUxXipEZLyUJQLasfwHFQaYW0PLCQLT7Jz2c7ZQnI2FN3n1554lGZJssKew8B7R4Ohgh8tj27B6WK0d9el5jlMg1vgW9u6BJ-B_RgBzv8o-MZOsQbFatER00YUvWt5AUL-ZXN4YhOffiwm-Qsur_7J9EECu4e37fbpLpRvFlyGjCrV5N_mvNw8m0C6ZVHL3FI2FWe4Cx1HtxpjxHAZjNJ1GBu59ULi9WBp-nCKkg6-XtxfN5aLpTqZvGVVezUgXcpxbsmNS7wx_RrgF5rUDZmEMaEaqWUUeLU9CY_2fZUgBOK5N5fCVZeNtSMyTmaGuMTLy23zbJo8RnMmVDnrxSkQVQkzEAkdjKTwoTQwR6wCj7hW_A/zmQmtlOn_CCVhIEUFyMEOCarYAedi39A/19" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="贝森特表示，美国考虑取消对部分伊朗石油的制裁"&gt;美国正在考虑取消对部分伊朗石油的制裁，&lt;/a&gt;以缓和油价。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;如果发生这种情况，这将是一次非同寻常的干预，有效地扭转了唐纳德·特朗普总统自上任并撕毁与德黑兰核协议以来一直处于战略核心的政策。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;十多年来，伊朗的石油出口一直受到制裁，但最严厉的措施是在 2019 年特朗普第一任期内采取的。贝森特表示，该政策将适用于已经上市的伊朗原油。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;德黑兰尚未做出回应，尚不清楚这是否会对实际战争或其&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/FKlhAmlEPe3d6EMdhll-YV3ZCaQT6Bx3s0S8klJitsLMu3Tdya8lta9MtA7OLFpJLi-voDl68eoy7kyRgCzDCzOkS7QkYlv-3B9rVpJgQat9uCmcyTEe5d3ysHjy9HSbmm9n-9Rm9xfBzVLcePMeLOEoqEYTQq1DineF3KkhzADim3-PwfGTw4Q6NeyCJY1vUGjm6Q5sVeFkoHD0ZQx1diglHYp5EjafW4yU5tQClz8xxfRiuccZnT0NweZxRnbQCPEcM5dfjXkeRI0sJWIxGmNdWVoz8eqFFJkUHzV6-EJk2Dxv6cPpPbOST-4vz4cBJmTYF0SohCS5_iTm9wJqDDSgoZz43ziIM0D343H9fuz-8o9bE-LUBNjTcMaz_N6-azm3Xb6Pmy7sjSyCl_2MolqJThWUewTxBMpB76ODjjoAh7196yn3JMzdgaIz-7kpFkY_8oTu3ZcW1pggFJzY_57fIV-q7lgGobcl2qQEf6t4Wn6-X34m_2dnq-8MksbUX8bgTIWupV-1DCDMx1LTuQ/H7IgbeeNTk9JZ3IpW8n5nDZlQ9LE6nwg/19" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" tit