or: #00e;" target="_blank" title="美国监管机构公布放宽大银行资本规定的计划"&gt;释放数十亿美元的资金用于贷款、股票回购和股息&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;特朗普去年任命的美联储监管副主席米歇尔·鲍曼表示：“这些变化将加强我们的整体资本框架，在新制度下该框架将保持强劲。”&lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure style="margin: 20px 0;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/J4HE__8LlUtNC5MtzKAOBCiz3sserbGeQ036gEnTEPPa-yYcjZP4leFmlH0hvtHyle42IslgnYNNQsFc4nxwzJIY05sREEfZBbfaC_yh3k2WXGN0YbXKnwEGDZCQomaiCgmOPBr6Omsf4Xe3Dhe0apxJNT3vTmNw4tpmE5Nc9b2lITEs8QiyDh4Swjdn5sJux5Q9W2qXLiXjpD1719J-G6wPAPJiWEVvSnw3BfQ6n8pXam1VXbxuVNl_ugIcXdibvDc9IwpD9usNiDobzrt_1cpiaJaaw4cxWfDA_vxTkZr2uqhiYH1vOOeMyZhqc1vRxqDE9eWjGq6nQOirSxee8BzIRwjC_jv4E1k3C2dKeKsZK3hKbVSMkXS1fvl5zUkicU0aHSQaIfderXW46sM/zvXQQ26y7TCWhiRKbm3vRsv43vjbGk6s/18" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="580"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ihOiIh1mtBkE/v7/-1x-1.jpg" alt="Michelle Bowman, vice chair for supervision at the US Federal Reserve nominee for US President Donald Trump, speaks during a Senate Banking, Housing, and Urban Affairs Committee confirmation hearing in Washington, DC, US, on Thursday, April 10, 2025. Senators on both sides of the panel are likely to ask how Bowman plans to comply with an executive order that curbs the power of independent agencies, and are eager to hear how she will approach a plan that would require the country&amp;amp;#39;s largest lenders to hold significantly more capital to buffer against losses and a financial crisis. Photographer: Kent Nishimura&amp;amp;#x2F;Bloomberg" width="580"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="美国总统唐纳德·特朗普提名人的美联储监管副主席米歇尔·鲍曼于 2025 年 4 月 10 日星期四在美国华盛顿特区举行的参议院银行、住房和城市事务委员会确认听证会上发表讲话。该委员会双方的参议员可能会问鲍曼计划如何遵守限制独立机构权力的行政命令，并渴望听到她将如何实施一项需要美国最大贷款机构的计划持有更多资本来缓冲损失和金融危机。摄影师：肯特·西村&amp;amp;#x2F;彭博社" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ihOiIh1mtBkE/